column2: SELECT m.int_id, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, m.z as redshift1, s.bestobjid, s.z as redshift, s.class as specClass, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2, o.petroRad_r, o.petroRadErr_r, o.u, o.err_u, o.extinction_u, o.g, o.err_g, o.extinction_g, o.r, o.err_r, o.extinction_r, o.i, o.err_i, o.extinction_i, o.z, o.err_z, o.extinction_z, o.petroMag_u, o.petroMagErr_u, o.petroMag_g, o.petroMagErr_g, o.petroMag_r, o.petroMagErr_r, o.petroMag_i, o.petroMagErr_i, o.petroMag_z, o.petroMagErr_z, o.petroR5#_r, o.petroR5#Err_r, o.petroR9#_r, o.petroR9#Err_r into mydb.TheBeans_#_newer FROM MyDB.TheBeansNew AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = o.objid LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON e.specobjid = s.specobjid
